  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/1a9903efcb87c88ee26873cefb017a8f.poster.avif?t=1760442801\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/1a9903efcb87c88ee26873cefb017a8f.webm?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/1a9903efcb87c88ee26873cefb017a8f.mp4?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a whimsical journey in Tiny Kingdom, where your story begins on a quaint farm that, through your actions, evolves into a magnificent kingdom. This enchanting card-based city-builder invites you to shape your realm, one card at a time, on a serene island canvas. Immerse yourself in a cute and cozy medieval world where every decision matters and every card holds the promise of new adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/c74abff075a1b9395a9cea97ea835ae4.webp?t=1760442801\" width=610 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically place cards. Each card interacts with adjacent tiles, creating charming synergies and expanding your kingdom’s potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/746f5ca4b0f33653774f3040d5e32a53.poster.avif?t=1760442801\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/746f5ca4b0f33653774f3040d5e32a53.webm?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/746f5ca4b0f33653774f3040d5e32a53.mp4?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/bff27f5f6707db2d754dae1203d517b5.webp?t=1760442801\" width=610 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new cards and opportunities as you build. Maximize your placements to ensure your deck grows and evolves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/f11153102e09701fe2bf2ec0e5af62e4.poster.avif?t=1760442801\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/f11153102e09701fe2bf2ec0e5af62e4.webm?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/f11153102e09701fe2bf2ec0e5af62e4.mp4?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/f939c07b6da278d8a5606a98daf5105c.avif?t=1760442801\" width=610 height=247 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/1a9903efcb87c88ee26873cefb017a8f.poster.avif?t=1760442801\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/1a9903efcb87c88ee26873cefb017a8f.webm?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/1a9903efcb87c88ee26873cefb017a8f.mp4?t=1760442801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a whimsical journey in Tiny Kingdom, where your story begins on a quaint farm that, through your actions, evolves into a magnificent kingdom. This enchanting card-based city-builder invites you to shape your realm, one card at a time, on a serene island canvas. Immerse yourself in a cute and cozy medieval world where every decision matters and every card holds the promise of new adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/c74abff075a1b9395a9cea97ea835ae4.webp?t=1760442801\" width=610 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategically place cards. Each card interacts with adjacent tiles, creating charming synergies and expanding your kingdom’s potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/746f5ca4b0f33653774f3040d5e32a53.poster.avif?t=1760442801\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2438260/extras/746f5ca4b0f33653774f3040d5e32a53.webm?